{"tid":600994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺廁所後面有sensor好反智","createTime":"2018-03-21T23:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T05:31:19.000Z","uid":17958,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"188db26a07c73478f356ffe713bfcd306a070d2d","tid":600994,"uid":17958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T23:58:42.000Z","msg":"次次去親商場廁所 廁所板後面有距離沖廁sensor都覺得好on9<br />\n通常去出面廁所屙屎 一定唔會坐晒成塊板<br />\n因為好多撚屌屙尿唔拎起塊板 又散彈咁射污糟晒<br />\n揀無可揀唯有坐前少少屙屎<br />\n個垃圾sensor收到有人坐就著<br />\n但個身烏前少少佢就當人走左 <br />\n屌你老母我未屙完就沖廁 好似日本d廁所洗屎忽咁<br />\n但用緊d屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條屎屙到一半仆街都唔知起唔起身好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦 到真正屙完 要起身抆屎<br />\n屌佢我未抆完就沖廁 留低d抆屎廁紙係到<br />\n又要沖多一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用sensor其實係衛生 但極浪費水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個情況只限於放正板背嘅sensor<br />\n放側邊用手fing嘅sensor唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e622e1fd80fa71bae3ba6ce9f8dc31f630a6f47","tid":600994,"uid":72688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T00:01:23.000Z","msg":"如果唔係你以為帶memo紙入廁所做乜呀？抆屎呀？"},{"pid":"6cdae8b67f919dbde427b07033aa9417874a7d87","tid":600994,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T00:13:13.000Z","msg":"次次痾屎都用廁紙冚撚住個sensor先<br />\n好鳩煩成日痾到一半自動沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135ea4a8582c341c271548cc39786c37485c9d6c","tid":600994,"uid":117302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T00:14:40.000Z","msg":"尿兜個sensor都好on9, 一行埋去未屙就沖，水力又太大，彈到周身都係水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc4a6dfe6742d33faef42cadbf19ef2a08997c9","tid":600994,"uid":9265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"德福商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痾痾下屎 個袋底濕既"}]}